{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2109027, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 409700, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "西亚国际地位显然更高吧", "timestamp": 1626859264, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2109036, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 409700, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "毕竟代表一种宗教，一种语言，还和石油息息相关", "timestamp": 1626859316, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2109053, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 409700, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我以为任意八国都行", "timestamp": 1626859469, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2109054, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 409700, "reply_to": 2109036, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 对，我看以前的说法是算葡语的，那会还是金砖四国的概念，现在阿拉伯世界体量上来了说法又变了", "timestamp": 1626859493, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2109068, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 409700, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "。。。我随便精通八种语言都可以说精通八国语言，没有这样的规定。", "timestamp": 1626859633, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2109079, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 409700, "reply_to": 2109068, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 有的，你看动漫电影八国语言翻译和景点路标牌，语言和国际地位是分不开的", "timestamp": 1626859733, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2109093, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 409700, "reply_to": 2109079, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 但是有人说自己精通八国语言，当然不意味着就是特定的那八种。我会八个语言当然也可以说自己精通八国语言。没有任何逻辑问题。", "timestamp": 1626859806, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2109109, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 409700, "reply_to": 2109093, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 这个我知道，我问的是普遍的说法", "timestamp": 1626859864, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2109117, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 409700, "reply_to": 2109109, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 没有见过有关“精通八国语言”的规定。。。与其这样，不如直接问最广泛使用的八种语言，不用强行加tag。个人意见。", "timestamp": 1626859930, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 1, "pid": 409700, "reply": 9, "tag": null, "text": "一般说的精通八国语言是指联合国的六个+德日，还是去掉阿拉伯语加上葡语啊，感觉葡语跟西语还是很多相通的地方，本土也颓了，其实也就是看西亚和巴西哪个世界地位更高了", "timestamp": 1626859169, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1626859928, "url": "", "vote": {}}}